flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
SPHEAL is much faster rolling than 
walking to get around. When groups of
this POKMON eat, they all clap at once to show their pleasure. Because of this,
their mealtimes are noisy.

SPHEAL always travels by rolling
around on its ball-like body. When the
season for ice floes arrives, this POKMON can be seen rolling about on
ice and crossing the sea.

It is completely covered with plushy fur.
As a result, it never feels the cold even
when it is rolling about on ice floes or
diving in the sea.

Its body is covered in fluffy fur. The
fur keeps it from feeling cold while
it is rolling on ice.

ils applaudissent tous en mme temps pour montrer

Seemops kann schneller rollen als laufen. Wenn Gruppen
dieses Pokmon zusammen essen, klatschen sie gleichzeitig,
um ihre Freude zu zeigen. Deswegen sind ihre Mahlzeiten

Spheal se desplaza por el suelo ms rpido rodando que
caminando. Cuando come con otros de su especie, todos se
ponen a aplaudir para expresar su alegra. Por eso, a veces
son algo escandalosos.

Spheal si muove molto pi velocemente rotolando che non
camminando. Quando si raggruppano per mangiare, questi
Pokmon sbattono le zampette per dimostrare la loro gioia.
I loro pasti sono molto rumorosi.

Seemops bewegt sich fort, indem es seinen ballartigen Krper
herumrollt. Wenn Eisschollen auftauchen, kann man dieses
Pokmon dabei beobachten, wie es ber das Eis rollt und
das Meer berquert.

Spheal se desplaza siempre rodando gracias al cuerpo
esfrico que tiene. Al comenzar la poca glacial, es fcil verle
rodando por superficies heladas y atravesando el mar.

Spheal si muove sempre rotolando sul corpo a pallone.
Nella stagione del disgelo lo si vede rotolare da una lastra
di ghiaccio allaltra per attraversare il mare.
